    "description": "<strong>Ascend The Well</strong> 是一款具有挑战性的平台游戏，您需要使用抓钩爬上井。爬上去可能非常棘手，这就是为什么您需要确保抓钩射击准确的原因。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/031bd715b8145bd532aee9bfa509e304.poster.avif?t=1725631446\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/031bd715b8145bd532aee9bfa509e304.webm?t=1725631446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/031bd715b8145bd532aee9bfa509e304.mp4?t=1725631446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>没有检查点</strong><br><br>尽量不要摔倒，因为您可能会摔得很远。根据您摔倒的位置，您可能会很幸运，只摔倒一点。或者你没那么幸运，你可能会一直摔到起点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/056f452a759cdd93c4ca2aaacb02c3d2.poster.avif?t=1725631446\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/056f452a759cdd93c4ca2aaacb02c3d2.webm?t=1725631446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094490/extras/056f452a759cdd93c4ca2aaacb02c3d2.mp4?t=1725631446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要功能</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>抓钩</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 个独特区域</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>计时器和抓钩计数器</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 个成就</li></ul>",
